                    </div>
				
                <div class="post__body post__content">
					<div><h4>Notes on life</h4>
<figure><img alt="" src="http://www.theawl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1ViXUA6cc6SuPdpKWZkC0sg.jpeg"></figure>
